children.subject: Our prerequisites for this spring were either 61A or Data 8, and we did not enforce this. We are still reworking the course for the fall semester. Stay tuned for the student application!
What are the (enforced / recommended) pre-requisites for the decal?
hi! I'd love to join the course this semester as a student, but I just wanted to check if leetcode 101 will be online or in-person.

history.content:
Hey everyone!

Our first semester of the IAT (Leetcode 101) Decal was a bigger hit than expected, and we're now looking for more people to join course staff. If you liked 61B/170, have around 4 hours a week to spare, and enjoy teaching and mentoring, we'd love to meet you! Check out our website at leetcode101.com to see what we've covered this semester!

The application will remain open until June 30, 11:59pm. If selected, we will reach out for an interview later in July/August. 

NOTE: THIS IS THE COURSE STAFF APPLICATION. Student enrollment applications will come out later, near the start of the semester. 

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd047ABUqUtO1IaZtxhAjDR7irm-kAhio2L3A9eFoNBkq6zFw/viewform?usp=sf_link
